掩興奮之情。<br />\n<br />\nPuyocha ぷよちゃ Facebook<br />\nPuyocha ぷよちゃ Twitter （18禁注意）<br />\n<br />\n請大家多多支持香港漫畫家～<br />\n延伸閱讀：香港漫畫家「楪廷戸」獲得贏得週刊少年Jump手塚賞！"},{"pid":"8a31caa331925a9744979366065db2b876950928","tid":1828635,"uid":28792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:50:33.000Z","msg":"唔好上咗岸唔落返嚟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢啲泳衣好J到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3051c22a1dd1bb03139e38d50fd18e95100cee","tid":1828635,"uid":48330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恭喜晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a1d762713d3226eb5f77def7fcacb1199d706c","tid":1828635,"uid":48330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a31caa331925a9744979366065db2b876950928","tid":1828635,"uid":28792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:50:33.000Z","msg":"唔好上咗岸唔落返嚟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢啲泳衣好J到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"單行本好好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a995ac7712818d26ff6a746c0442371c944002a","tid":1828635,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"刀劍反共"},{"pid":"d7d9bde72ed0cbd44f212a23fbf0ef863df2fc1c","tid":1828635,"uid":37902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:04:52.000Z","msg":"叫司徒劍橋畫"},{"pid":"9bf5d84d21bfcae5b2db4ba687e61c56383c31a0","tid":1828635,"uid":203592,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"仲以為係猿生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f233004fe626c